high_descs: In the toilet room turn around and take right to the sink.
Head towards the sink and reach for the mango.
Pick the fruit from the sink.
Keep the mango on top of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Pick the Mango and keep it on top of the Sink.

high_descs: Turn right to the wall and turn right to the sink side.
Head towards the sink take the mango from the sink.
Turn left and turn right to the sink.
Place the mango on the sink top.
anns.task_desc: Take the Mango from the Sink and place it on the top of the Sink

high_descs: Turn around and walk forward to the bathroom sink
Pick up the mango from the sink
Put the mango down on the back edge of the sink
anns.task_desc: Put the mango on the back of the sink
